  "text": "All animal experiments were carried out according to the regulations of the local animal research council and legislation of the State of Lower Saxony. High-copy number B6/SJLTg(SOD1 * G93A)1Gur/J (labeled as SOD1 G93A in the following text) [CITATION_1] were obtained from Jackson Labs (Stock Number 002726; Bar Harbor, USA). The colony was maintained by crossing B6/SJL males harboring the transgene with wild-type B6/SJL females. Housing of animals was performed under a 12 h light/12 h dark cycle with free access to food and water.",
  "correct_citation": {
